Sub-Store Cloudflare is a Cloudflare Worker application for subscription
aggregation and cloud-side routing templates.

The Worker code, deployment tooling, and documentation in this repository are
distributed under the license in LICENSE. There is no warranty.

The frontend in frontend/ is a trimmed Cloudflare-native edition based on the
original Sub-Store frontend experience and remains accompanied by
frontend/LICENSE.

